@{
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<style>
    /* --- General Privacy Page Styles (White & Blue Theme) --- */
    .privacy-page-content {
        padding: 30px 0; /* Reduced padding */
        background-color: #f4f7fa; /* Very light background */
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; /* Clean, modern font */
        line-height: 1.5; /* Slightly tighter line height */
    }

    .policy-header-section {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 30px; /* Reduced margin */
        padding: 15px;
        background-color: #e6f3ff; /* Very light blue header background */
        border-radius: 6px;
        border-bottom: 3px solid #007bff; /* Blue accent line */
    }

        .policy-header-section h1 {
            color: #007bff; /* Primary Blue for headings */
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 3px;
            font-size: 1.8em; /* Reduced heading size */
        }

            .policy-header-section h1 i {
                margin-right: 8px;
            }

    .last-updated {
        font-style: italic;
        color: #6c757d;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        font-size: 0.9em;
    }

    .intro-statement {
        font-size: 1.0em; /* Slightly smaller font */
        color: #343a40;
    }

    /* --- Policy Sections --- */
    .policy-sections {
        max-width: 800px; /* Reduced max width for compactness */
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 25px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border: 1px solid #ced4da;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }

        .policy-sections section {
            margin-bottom: 25px; /* Reduced margin */
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }

            .policy-sections section:last-child {
                border-bottom: none;
            }

        .policy-sections h2 {
            color: #007bff; /* Primary Blue */
            border-left: 4px solid #007bff; /* Blue accent line */
            padding-left: 12px;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-size: 1.4em; /* Reduced heading size */
        }

        .policy-sections p {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #495057;
            font-size: 0.95em; /* Smaller paragraph font */
        }

        /* List Styling for clarity */
        .policy-sections ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding-left: 0;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }

            .policy-sections ul li {
                position: relative;
                margin-bottom: 8px;
                padding-left: 25px;
                font-size: 0.95em; /* Smaller list font */
                color: #495057;
            }

                .policy-sections ul li::before {
                    content: '\f058'; /* Checkmark icon */
                    font-family: 'Font Awesome 5 Free';
                    font-weight: 900;
                    color: #28a745; /* Keeping a subtle green for 'success' (security) checkmarks */
                    position: absolute;
                    left: 0;
                    top: 0;
                }

    /* Blockquote for contact notes */
    .contact-note {
        background-color: #f8f9fa; /* Light gray background */
        border-left: 5px solid #007bff; /* Blue border */
        padding: 12px;
        margin: 15px 0;
        font-style: italic;
        color: #007bff; /* Blue text */
        border-radius: 4px;
        font-size: 0.9em;
    }

        .contact-note i {
            margin-right: 6px;
            color: #007bff;
        }
</style>
<div class="privacy-page-content">

    <div class="container policy-header-section">
        <h1><i class="fas fa-user-shield"></i> LinguaLink Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="last-updated">
            **Last Updated:** December 30, 2025
        </p>
        <p class="intro-statement">
            LinguaLink is committed to protecting the privacy of our users. This policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website and use our language learning services.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="container policy-sections">

        <section>
            <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
            <p>We collect personal data that you voluntarily provide to us when registering, participating in activities, or contacting us.</p>
            <ul>
                <li>**Personal Identification Data:** Name, email address, phone number (if provided), and account credentials.</li>
                <li>**Payment Data:** Credit/debit card numbers (handled securely by payment processors, we do not store full details).</li>
                <li>**Usage Data:** Information about how you use the platform, including courses started, progress, test scores, and learning preferences.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p>We use your information for various purposes:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>To **Facilitate Account Creation and Logon**.</li>
                <li>To **Provide, Operate, and Maintain** our services and personalized learning content.</li>
                <li>To **Process Payments** and manage transactions.</li>
                <li>To **Improve User Experience** and develop new features based on usage patterns.</li>
                <li>To **Communicate** with you about service updates, security alerts, and marketing offers (if consented).</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>3. Sharing Your Information</h2>
            <p>Your personal information is kept secure and is never shared with third parties for marketing purposes without your explicit consent. We may share data only with:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>**Service Providers:** Third parties who perform services for us (e.g., payment processing, hosting, analytics).</li>
                <li>**Legal Requirements:** When required by law or to protect the rights and safety of LinguaLink and our users.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
            <p>We use administrative, technical, and physical security measures to help protect your personal information. While we strive to protect your data, please remember that no method of transmission over the Internet is 100% secure.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>5. Your Privacy Rights</h2>
            <p>Depending on your location, you may have the right to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>**Access** the personal data we hold about you.</li>
                <li>**Request Correction** of inaccurate data.</li>
                <li>**Request Deletion** of your personal data (subject to legal obligations).</li>
                <li>**Opt-out** of receiving promotional communications.</li>
            </ul>
            <blockquote class="contact-note">
                <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> To exercise any of these rights, please contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@lingualink.com">privacy@lingualink.com</a>.
            </blockquote>
        </section>

    </div>

</div>